import React from 'react'
import { render } from 'react-dom'
import {Provider} from 'react-redux'
//Provider是react-redux提供的组件
import App from './App'
import store from './store'
window.store = store
console.log(store)
render(
    <Provider store ={store}>
        <App/>
    </Provider>
    ,
    document.querySelector('#root')
)
